name: WOOF
description: WOOF is an ERC-20 token used within the WOOF Labs ecosystem to empower our decentralized community WOOF Token serves several purposes: NFT Trading on Open Waters at 0% Marketplace fees WOOF token can be used to buy and sell NFTs on CoreDAO Blockchain on WOOF Labs Native NFT Marketplace Open Waters at 0% Marketplace fees We also have our own Swap on CoreDAO known as "WOOF Swap" where we have Liquidity Farms for WOOF which helps maintain good amount of liquidity All the current and future web3 platforms build by our WOOF Labs Ecosystem does and will utilize WOOF token in some way. Currently WOOF is #1 Token on CoreDAO blockchain in terms of daily volume.
